                                              Dennis Geronimus, <em>Piero di Cosimo: Visions Beautiful and Strange</em>, Yale University Press (U.S.) (New Haven and London, 2006), pp. 21, 82-83, 100-106, 125, 302 n. 184, and 317 n. 104; repr. in color p. 103 as Fig. 71.
                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Stephan Wolohojian and Alvin L. Clark, Jr., <em>Harvard Art Museum/ Handbook</em>, ed. Stephan Wolohojian, Harvard Art Museum (Cambridge, 2008), p. 64, repr.
                             </p>
